{"tid":556463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大埔翻巴士】肇事車長大起底 自稱巴士迷 4年前高速掟彎掃毀5米欄","createTime":"2018-02-10T13:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T13:39:23.000Z","uid":78546,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ac91c0635cde80974f684474b5402e02b07ae486","tid":556463,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:21:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180210&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57817715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180210%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57817715&d=mnHpIPXg%2BssSCV9o%2BYI3CROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=c43b5578\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180210%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57817715&h=63835c17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180210&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57817715</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大埔公路傍晚發生19人死亡的特大車禍中，有認識肇事車長的人士致電《蘋果》報料，指出該名車長花名「口罩明」，自稱「巴士迷」，活躍於多個網上巴士迷群組，曾在網上平台留言：「介紹下自己背景先，年近三十，冇樣，冇身材，冇車，冇樓，有信用卡，冇學歷，月入唔過兩萬，少講野(嘢)，睇場合怕醜，睇場合內向，消費模式極度慳皮，唔應洗(使)既(嘅)唔洗(使)，應該要洗(使)既(嘅)都可以唔洗(使)，放假冇野(嘢)做可以係反正都有野(嘢)做，不如去開工搵多日錢&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n據知，「口罩明」愛好揸巴士，一向慳儉的他早前更不惜花錢買入一部舊式「熱九」，還改名「MING CHAN」不時在網上炫耀。不過有認識他的巴士迷指出，「口罩明」駕駛態度相當有問題，更直言：「佢遲早出事，今次終於搞單大鑊嘢！」原來2014年8月，由姓陳車長駕駛的九巴亦曾發生交通意外，造成一名途人及一名乘客受傷。<br />\n<br />\n記者找到當日的報道，當時27歲的他駕駛一部46X九巴，當駛至葵芳港鐵站時，疑轉彎車速太快失控，掃毀路邊5米鐵欄及一條石柱才停下，車頭嚴重損毀。當年車禍時，該姓陳車長才剛入職九巴7個月，當時車上乘客僅三人，其中一名乘客事後更因不滿車長駕駛態度，直言：「我腳痛都落去鬧個巴士佬，離晒譜！」"},{"pid":"0ed46a371bfaeb1d3bd157f7ba93778f41b53aac","tid":556463,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:23:05.000Z","msg":"巴膠.."},{"pid":"b7732eb69598bf3cc80fa1a0b1074e4aa430b078","tid":556463,"uid":21629,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:32:01.000Z","msg":"巴膠好似無咩幾個係正常"},{"pid":"0d55e7f11a7cb784bbeea0a67430fe3fd9aad73a","tid":556463,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ed46a371bfaeb1d3bd157f7ba93778f41b53aac","tid":556463,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:23:05.000Z","msg":"巴膠.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:35:41.000Z","msg":"X2"},{"pid":"8270c4ca140246f348935d46382850f629f37588","tid":556463,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7732eb69598bf3cc80fa1a0b1074e4aa430b078","tid":556463,"uid":21629,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:32:01.000Z","msg":"巴膠好似無咩幾個係正常"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4e6d4d01ed7558bb9fa52ac9ac18246d582f63","tid":556463,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:39:23.000Z","msg":"仲有另一個9A狀元 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130520/18265592\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130520%2F18265592&d=mnHpIPXg%2BssSCV9o%2BYI3CROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=68059ba4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130520%2F18265592&h=f23b935e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130520/18265592</a>"}]}